des:
Need a quick highlight of the live cricket score? 
Let Alexa bring you the score highlights for live cricket matches.

Cricket score is a simple one dialogue cricket score skill.
The skill can be used with following invocations - 
"Alexa, tell cricket score", 
"Alexa, cricket score" or 
"Alexa, open cricket score"
